t of all happy childhood memories.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aChildren with disabilitiesxGuidebooksxRecreationxConnecticut. 0aChildren with disabilitiesxRecreationzConnecticutvGuidebooks. 7aREFERENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aKaplan, Josiah David, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKaplan, Lawrence C., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030013077540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300130775423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300130775/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles